title: Rob Dyrdek: ON Dropping Out of School and Becoming an Entrepreneur
description: You may know Rob as a former pro skateboarder and the host of MTV’s Ridiculousness, but this conversation is going to show you inside his mind.He’s an incredible strategist, such a planner, someone who is so meticulous - something you don’t see in his persona in his shows.You’re going to see a completely different side of the one and only Rob Dyrdek.
author: onpurposepodcast@jayshetty.me (Jay Shetty)
